ata-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/apaszke\">@apaszke</a></p>", "body_text": "Are you sure offloading to the CPU is a good idea?\n\nIt means that CUDA code sometimes affect the state of the CPU RNG, but not the CUDA RNG\nIt adds a CUDA synchronization point. (I'm not sure if the thrust code synchronizes)\n\n@soumith @apaszke", "body": "Are you sure offloading to the CPU is a good idea?\r\n\r\n1. It means that CUDA code sometimes affect the state of the CPU RNG, but not the CUDA RNG\r\n2. It adds a CUDA synchronization point. (I'm not sure if the thrust code synchronizes)\r\n\r\n@soumith @apaszke "}